magnetic sheet back to back.</source>
        <target>crwdns11209:0crwdne11209:0</target>
        <note>Context: XPath: /ul/li</note>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="11210" identifier="3fb7832ac822733febaaa2e5a0b77d9f">
        <source>Paper (non-magnetic) cards can be made by cutting up a sheet of light card
that is a different colour on each side.</source>
        <target>crwdns11210:0crwdne11210:0</target>
        <note>Context: XPath: /ul/li</note>
